name: Shiba
description: Shiba was created by one of the OG Shiba whales and influencer: @shiba. The aftermath of stories to be discussed on X spaces which lead to the rebirth of Shiba. Time to reverse time and shift responsibilities. It's the community taking matters into their own hands. Post-launch renounced contract access and liquidity burn. The long anticipation is coming to an end.. Everyone is aching for a new leader.
